  "text": "Proof. The n = 1 version is in [CITATION_1] . Simply notice that the minimizer \u03b1 V \u03b1 \u03be \u03b1 is such that each V \u03b1 is a linear combination of \u2206 \u03b2 's. Non-degeneracy comes from the fact that",
